@startuml Smart Reference Proxy Core Components

interface Object {
    + operation(): void
}

class RealObject implements Object {
    + operation(): void
}

class SmartProxy implements Object {
    - realObject: RealObject
    - referenceCount: int
    - lastAccessTime: Date
    + SmartProxy()
    + operation(): void
    - updateReferenceCount(): void
    - logAccess(): void
}

note right: Tracks object usage
note right: Reference counting, logging

SmartProxy *-- RealObject
Client ..> SmartProxy : uses

@enduml
